OL,3,CGuernsey veteran receives Ukrainian
OL,4,Caward for clearing mines
OL,6,FBen says he is humbled to receive the
OL,7,Faward and credits his whole team.
OL,9,FHe told ITV News: "I think recognition
OL,10,Fof the work that we do is very, very
OL,11,Fimportant. To be awarded the support
OL,12,Fcross by the military here is
OL,13,Fincredibly humbling."
OL,15,FUkrainian Dr Yaraslav Stefak is an
OL,16,Fanaesthetist at the Princess Elizabeth
OL,17,FHospital in Guernsey. He has praised
OL,18,FBen's actions, saying: "What he's
OL,19,Fdoing, teaching people to the mine
OL,20,Fterritories is impressive.
