OL,3,CGuernsey veteran receives Ukrainian
OL,4,Caward for clearing mines
OL,6,F"The death rate in Ukraine is quite
OL,7,Fhigh from mines. I believe in the last
OL,8,Fyear there were about 20,000 incidents
OL,9,Famong the civilian population and of
OL,10,Fthose, about 10% or 15% died.
OL,12,F"The rest sustained severe trauma, so
OL,13,Fthis is a massive problem."
OL,15,FThe work of Friends of Ukraine is far
OL,16,Ffrom over, Ben said that an estimated
OL,17,F15,000 to 20,000 'deminers' are needed
OL,18,Fto clear the mines in Ukraine.
